    <p>
        The close icon is rendered with a CSS <code>mask-image</code> tinted with <code>currentcolor</code>, so it adapts
        to the surrounding text color automatically &mdash; the former <code>White</code> parameter no longer exists.
        Use <code>data-bs-theme="dark"</code> on the button or a parent element to invert it explicitly.
